","msg":"1945年8月14日，中國國民政府代表宋子文等人在蔣介石的授權下與蘇聯簽訂《中蘇友好同盟條約》，中國政府聲明「日本戰敗之後，如外蒙古的公民投票證實這種獨立願望，中國政府當承認外蒙古的獨立，並以現在的邊界作為國界。」同年10月20日，外蒙古獨立公投結果公布，97.8%的公民贊成外蒙古獨立。1946年1月5日，中華民國政府正式承認外蒙古獨立[20]。<br />\n<br />\n中華人民共和國在1949年10月16日和蒙古人民共和國建交，確認了外蒙古獨立。"},{"pid":"036c7535ed9e04e7f332f27882c9c7243eed77a3","tid":2181633,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"坦克碌豬"},{"pid":"706119a0172b8307b75af848357ff60bfca5ff13","tid":2181633,"uid":353635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a182686ab6ecc387748da936d984902bdd36bb85","tid":2181633,"uid":228868,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T17:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遲早有內蒙集中營"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"內蒙有外蒙親兄弟幫手<br />\n俄國又同外蒙frd<br />\n覺得難d敢搞到新疆咁"},{"pid":"245161bcdac08292ba6aceb79f994c60f69f49e3","tid":2181633,"uid":331739,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T17:36:10.000Z","msg":"中國真係好撚最鐘意做啲表面嘢<br />\n喺啲網站同火車站加啲蒙古文扮尊重多元<br />\n實則係唔比學校教同打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0930bfa50664dc5035b8f97aaa0254824db80b","tid":2181633,"uid":39911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T17:36:57.000Z","msg":"又可以準備集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9746677a25faba1d91c8accc1ccc75ccd280b1","tid":2181633,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T17:38:22.000Z","msg":"舒服<br />\n<br />\n最好兩敗俱傷"},{"pid":"fed363addf6aebb9302f51f58578f51512405004","tid":2181633,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9a23f5573ce5a668ca8381d2906e2e8428d3aea","tid":2181633,"uid":81273,"like":12,"dislike